      <odd id="aspace_83cf5abc2b1de543d70ff9bb4f9a8f5c">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 13-E-3 (YRG 13-E-3), Records of the fellows of Calhoun College.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_d2e95e1524568ead502d4f728db034d4">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from Calhoun College, 2008.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_fba739e7b8c4f2355e2ecb072cf1d7da">
